// http://stackoverflow.com/questions/39729402/how-to-make-a-parallel-join-on-two-tables-and-order-result-by-creation-date

#input

| idal | idaction | dt                  |
|---------------------------------------|
| 5    |        6 | 2016-09-23 15:02:50 |
| 5    |        7 | 2016-09-23 16:00:00 |
| 5151 |        7 | 2016-09-01 00:00:00 |
| 5151 |        6 | 2016-12-01 15:35:34 |

#output


| idal | idaction | dt                  |
|---------------------------------------|
| 5    |        7 | 2016-09-23 16:00:00 |
| 5151 |        6 | 2016-12-01 15:35:34 |

# constraint
{
	"constants": [],
	"aggregation_functions": ["max"]
}

#solution

Select B.b, C.c
From A
LEFT OUTER JOIN B ON B.a_id = A.id
LEFT OUTER JOIN C ON C.a_id = A.id
ORDER BY B.creation_Date,C.creation_Date ;